# Phase F.5 (ADR-031) — dead-letter quarantine should NEVER be checked in.
# Real path is /var/lib/automecanik-rag/quarantine/ (Docker volume) ; this guard
# prevents accidental commit if the service is ever run with cwd inside the repo.
