# Runtime freshness manifest — rewritten every sync run with a fresh `synced_at`
# and read *from disk* by RagMirrorFreshnessService (36h mirror-freshness SLO).
# It is runtime observability state, NOT versioned content. Tracking it turned
# every hourly no-op sync into a `synced-from-wiki:` churn commit. Untracked here
# (companion: monorepo scripts/cron/sync-rag-from-wiki.sh excludes it too).
knowledge/.last-sync.json
